{"id":139565,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/西藏-拉萨起义52周年大昭寺屋顶武警戒备/","date":"2011-03-12T04:02:04Z","modified":"2011-03-12T04:02:04Z","title":"西藏: 拉萨起义52周年大昭寺屋顶武警戒备","content":"<p><div>\n        拉萨起义52周年大昭寺屋顶武警戒备      </div>\n<div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"257\" src=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_43_large/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/2011%E5%B9%B43%E6%9C%8810%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%A8%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B7%E6%BB%A1%E9%83%BD%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81.jpg\" title=\"\" width=\"344\" /></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>流亡尼泊尔藏民2011年3月10日在加德满都示威</div>\n<p> <span>路透社照片</span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n            作者 <a href=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/auteur/%E6%B3%95%E5%B9%BF\" rel=\"nofollow\">法广</a>          </div>\n<p>今天是拉萨起义52周年纪念日和3.14事件3周年临近，拉萨街头气氛开始紧张，军警高度戒备。自由亚洲网站引述当地消息人士称，军警在拉萨大昭寺屋顶设立了岗哨，持枪戒备。为防止发生示威，军警还在周三进驻西藏大学。</p>\n<p>\n�</p>\n</p></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>西藏当局上周还下令禁止境外记者进入西藏，同时在街道，路口及城乡结合部，设立哨卡，盘查进入拉萨的外地藏人，并在深夜搜查旅馆。<br />\n�</p>\n</p></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n        关键词 <a href=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/tag/%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F\" rel=\"nofollow\">西藏</a>      </div>\n</p></div>\n<div></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LQEkZEZ_A9UEmY3-s1AiNSLesaU/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LQEkZEZ_A9UEmY3-s1AiNSLesaU/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LQEkZEZ_A9UEmY3-s1AiNSLesaU/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LQEkZEZ_A9UEmY3-s1AiNSLesaU/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/RFICN/~4/OElkATvMwJM\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):ziyouwangluo2011ATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[19955,8643]}